@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam boxPadding 10

box "Orchestrator" #F9F9F9
    participant "EvaluationAgent" as Orch
end box

box "Agents" #E6F3FF
    participant "Architect" as Arch order 20
    participant "Manager" as Mgr order 30
    participant "Evaluation Team" as Eval order 40
    participant "Customer" as Cust order 50
end box

== Phase 1: Architecture Extraction ==
Orch -> Arch: Identify Architectural Approaches
activate Arch

    Arch -> Cust: Request System Constraints/Details
    activate Cust
    Cust --> Arch: System Description Data
    deactivate Cust

Arch --> Orch: Architectural Approaches (JSON)
deactivate Arch

' note right of Orch: Orchestrator syncs "Approaches"\nto Manager & Eval Team Knowledge Bases

== Phase 2: Utility Tree Generation ==
Orch -> Mgr: Generate Utility Tree
activate Mgr

    group Internal Review Protocol
        Mgr -> Arch: Validate Technical Feasibility
        activate Arch
        Arch --> Mgr: Approval or Critique
        deactivate Arch
    end

Mgr --> Orch: Utility Tree (JSON)
deactivate Mgr

' note right of Orch: Orchestrator syncs "Utility Tree"\nto Eval Team Knowledge Base

== Phase 3: Scenario Generation ==
Orch -> Mgr: Generate & Prioritize Scenarios
activate Mgr
Mgr --> Orch: Scenarios (JSON)
deactivate Mgr

== Phase 4: Analysis & Risk Assessment ==
Orch -> Eval: Identify Risks, Sensitivity, Tradeoffs
activate Eval

    Eval -> Arch: Request Technical Parameter Estimates
    activate Arch
    Arch --> Eval: Tech Specs / Clarifications
    deactivate Arch

Eval --> Orch: Analysis Records (JSON)
deactivate Eval

' == Completion ==
' Orch -> Orch: Compile & Save Final JSON Report

@enduml